import styled from "styled-components"

export const Style = styled.div`
      top: "50%",
      left: "50%",
      rigth: "auto",
      botton: "auto",
      marginRigth: "-50%",
      transform: "translate(-50%, -50%)",
      width: "90%",
      maxWidth: "369px",
      height: "50%",
      maxHeight: "342px",
      backgroundColor: "#212529",
      padding: "0px",
      display: "flex",
      flexDirection: "column",
      alignItens: "center",
    }`
